---
title: Honey Chili-Garlic Roasted Double Salmon with Pan-Fried Vegetables
description: We're practically drooling over this combination of luscious honey-chili-garlic roasted salmon, a juicy pan-fried veggie jumble and fluffy basmati rice. This is one for the (cook)books, folks!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF220725_R1011_W37_CA_RF152465-4_MB_Main_Low-54756745.jpg
